## PM2 — App Management

```bash
pm2 list                                    # See all running apps
pm2 restart energyapp-api                   # Restart backend
pm2 restart energyapp-frontend              # Restart frontend
pm2 logs energyapp-api --lines 30           # View backend logs
pm2 logs energyapp-api --err --lines 30     # View errors only
pm2 logs energyapp-frontend --lines 30      # View frontend logs
pm2 save                                    # Save current PM2 state
```

