## Git — Code Updates

```bash
cd /var/www/energyapp
git pull origin master                      # Pull latest code
git stash                                   # Stash local changes before pull
```

---

## After Code Changes

### Backend change (api folder):

```bash
cd /var/www/energyapp
git pull origin master
pm2 restart energyapp-api
```

### Frontend change (app folder):

```bash
cd /var/www/energyapp
git pull origin master
cd /var/www/energyapp/app
npm run build
pm2 restart energyapp-frontend
```

### Both changed:

```bash
cd /var/www/energyapp
git pull origin master
cd /var/www/energyapp/app
npm run build
pm2 restart energyapp-api
pm2 restart energyapp-frontend
```

