## Database

```bash
# Open MySQL
mysql -u root -p

# Run migrations (after fresh DB import)
mysql -u root -p energyapp < /var/www/energyapp/migrations.sql

# Drop and recreate database (fresh import)
mysql -u root -p -e "DROP DATABASE energyapp; CREATE DATABASE energyapp;"
mysql -u root -p energyapp < /root/u972964962_orbic.sql

# Clear billing data (if re-upload needed)
mysql -u root -p energyapp -e "DELETE FROM billing_exception_log; DELETE FROM billing_upload_log; DELETE FROM billing_extract_raw;"
```

