## Common Issues & Fixes

### API not starting (missing module):

```bash
pip install modulename
pm2 restart energyapp-api
```

### Frontend showing broken/no CSS:

```bash
cd /var/www/energyapp/app
npm run build
pm2 restart energyapp-frontend
```

### 413 File too large error:

```bash
nano /etc/nginx/sites-available/portal2
# Add inside server block: client_max_body_size 50M;
nginx -t && systemctl reload nginx
```

### Database field errors after fresh import:

```bash
mysql -u root -p energyapp < /var/www/energyapp/migrations.sql
```

### Check what's running on a port:

```bash
lsof -i :8002
```

### Kill process on a port:

```bash
fuser -k 8002/tcp
```

